data.description: 2Duplexes-flexible layout/configuration: FOUR 2Bed/2Bath units +1100sqft each. Or TWO 5Bed/4Bath units. A Block from the Ocean, Across from a park, Beach Access @ end of Street, abundant parking. Immaculate private grounds feature multiple Koi ponds; vinyl privacy fence allows each unit a private back yard. Buildings are newly remodeled, Concrete Block Stucco, Tile flooring in all units, Newer Central A/C & Roofs, updated electric. Nestled between the beach and Sandpiper Park multigenerational facility. Great Return
